OL,3,CDrone catches teenagers firing
OL,4,Cslingshots at trains in County Durham
OL,6,FPolice officers have used drones to
OL,7,Fidentify teenagers who were caught
OL,8,Ffiring slingshots at trains on a
OL,9,FCounty Durham railway line.
OL,11,FRail operator Northern says a number
OL,12,Fof its trains were damaged over the
OL,13,Fspace of a week in July when they were
OL,14,Fhit with projectiles.
OL,16,FAfter requesting support from Network
OL,17,FRail and British Transport Police,
OL,18,Fdrones were used to identify some of
OL,19,Fthose responsible.
