OL,3,CDrone catches teenagers firing
OL,4,Cslingshots at trains in County Durham
OL,6,FOfficers spoke to them about the
OL,7,Fdangers of their actions and took
OL,8,Ftheir personal details.
OL,10,FNo further slingshot incidents have
OL,11,Fbeen recorded since, according to
OL,12,FNorthern's crime reduction team.
OL,14,FInspector Mary-Anne Snowden, from
OL,15,FBritish Transport Police, said:
OL,16,F"Throwing objects at moving trains is
OL,17,Fhugely dangerous and an incredibly
OL,18,Firresponsible thing to do.
