OL,6,F"We continue to work with our industry
OL,7,Fpartners to prevent incidents like
OL,8,Fthese and identify those who are
OL,9,Fresponsible.
OL,11,F"Mindless acts of vandalism like this
OL,12,Fcan have potentially fatal
OL,13,Fconsequences, which is why we take
OL,14,Fevery incident seriously.
OL,16,F"Drones have demonstrated their
OL,17,Feffectiveness in tackling a variety of
OL,18,Fincidents through proactive and
OL,19,Freactive flights across the network
OL,20,Fgiving officers a bird's-eye view of
OL,21,Fany criminality on the railway."
