OL,6,FJason Wade, regional director for
OL,7,FNorthern, said: "We would like to
OL,8,Fthank the BTP officers who tracked
OL,9,Fdown the perpetrators and stopped them
OL,10,Ffrom targeting our services.
OL,12,F"We cannot tolerate reckless behaviour
OL,13,Fwhich puts the safety of our customers
OL,14,Fand train crew at risk.
OL,16,F"The consequences of a projectile
OL,17,Fhitting a train travelling at speed
OL,18,Fare potentially devastating."
