OL,6,FIn December, Northern said the number
OL,7,Fof dangerous attacks on its trains was
OL,8,Fdown almost 90 per cent on the
OL,9,Fprevious 12 months.
OL,11,FIt has also installed a further 600
OL,12,FCCTV cameras to monitor its stations,
OL,13,Fas well as 7,000 on its fleet of
OL,14,Ftrains and 1,300 body-worn cameras for
OL,15,Fits staff.
